STATE of North Carolina
v.
Gary Edwin BURNETT. No. 363P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 14, 2006. Gary Edwin Burnett, Pro Se. Daniel P. O'Brien, Assistant Attorney General, Thomas H. Lock, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 10th day of July 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Harnett County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th day of December 2006."
